_json.gridTitle: How I Built my DIY Floating Deck for less than $500
_json.description: Do you want a backyard deck and are you sick of waiting for someone else to do it? how i built a deck (by myself) for less than $500! With all the backyard ideas out there, I have a bunch of reasons why I HAD TO HAVE a floating deck. But the issue was, how can I get a DIY deck for cheap? Tutorials come in all different shapes and sizes, so I made my own! I designed, drilled, and now have a simple diy floating deck made with #momstrength and free online woodworking resources. #bigDECKener
